      "title": "Freight service to Tamil Nadu: Douglas",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Fisheries Minister Douglas Devananda has said that the Ministry of Defense has given permission to operate a freight ferry service between Kankesanthurai and Tamil Nadu in Jaffna."
      ],
